videos.headline: Ji'Ayir Brown comes up with end zone INT
videos.description: Ji'Ayir Brown gets the interception for Penn State as Arkansas can't come away with points on their opening drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ji’Ayir Brown comes up with end zone INT) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Raheim Sanders gives Razorbacks early lead
videos.description: Raheim Sanders caps off the 12-play drive with a rushing touchdown as Arkansas leads Penn State 7-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Raheim Sanders gives Razorbacks early lead) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Parker Washington makes sensational one-handed catch
videos.description: Parker Washington makes a fantastic leaping, one-handed snag for the Penn State first down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Parker Washington makes sensational one-handed catch) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clifford finds Lambert-Smith for the 42-yard TD
videos.description: KeAndre Lambert-Smith for the 42-yard touchdown as Penn State ties it 7-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clifford finds Lambert-Smith for the 42-yard TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State fails miserably on fake punt attempt
videos.description: Penn State runs a fake punt vs. Arkansas but fails miserably to convert as the punter heaves it nowhere near a receiver.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State fails miserably on fake punt attempt) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: K.J. Jefferson takes it in for the TD
videos.description: K.J. Jefferson takes the read-option in himself for the touchdown to put Arkansas up 14-10 over Penn State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (K.J. Jefferson takes it in for the TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Raheim Sanders scores second TD
videos.description: Raheim Sanders grabs his second touchdown on the day as Arkansas pads their lead to 14 points.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Raheim Sanders scores second TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Razorbacks defeat Penn State in the Outback Bowl
videos.description: Sam Pittman gets his first bowl win as head coach at Arkansas as the Razorbacks defeat Penn State 24-10.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Razorbacks defeat Penn State in the Outback Bowl) 2022/01/01 ESHEET SOTFULL
